HEADWORD: oil well
<hw>oil" well`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A well{3} from which petroleum is
or has been extracted; a well{3} drilled deeply into an oil-bearing
geological formation specifically for the purpose of obtaining
petroleum.</def>⟦br⟧
